                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The First Committee met on October 4 from 10:45 a. m. to 1:10 p. m.; for the
                    record, see U.N. document A/C.1/SR.352. Debate continued on the draft
                    resolutions and various amendments, preliminary to the voting which took place
                    at the afternoon session (see editorial note, <ref target="#pg_873">page
                        873</ref>).</p>
            </div>
        </body>
